                                                        @Model.TechnicalAbilities.Other[i].TechnologyUse
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        }
                                    </div>
                                }
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h4 class="h4">Questions I Like to Debate?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            ORM (Object Relation Mapping) vs Database Project Implementation?
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            MVC, a Design Pattern or an Architecture Pattern?
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
